# Fixture-scoped gitignore (CLAUDE.md memory: Fixture-scoped gitignore)
# WAL/shm sidecars and config / lock / log files spawn whenever a fake
# HOME points into this dir or a sqlite3 connection opens a fixture .db
# in WAL mode. Per-fixture .gitignore so the in-tree fixtures stay byte
# stable across `bin/cctally-test-all` runs and ad-hoc dev opens.
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
.config/
.local/
*.log
*.lock
